OL,4,G0325FThe Genesis Songbook
OL,5,     GThe line-up changed, the style
OL,6,     Gevolved, but the hits kept
OL,7,     Gcoming. From Peter Gabriel to
OL,8,     GPhil Collins, Invisible Touch to
OL,9,     GI Can't Dance, a documentary that
OL,10,     Gcharts the inspiration of Genesis.
OL,11,G0445FU2: Classic Albums
OL,12,     GThe Joshua Tree: Bono, The Edge,
OL,13,     GAdam Clayton, Larry Mullen and
OL,14,     Gproducers Brian Eno and Daniel
OL,15,     GLanois give an insight into the
OL,16,     Gmaking of their 1987 smash The
OL,17,     GJoshua Tree.
